# SuggaPlay Master Build (Mobile App)

Before building any mobile feature, read:

1. `docs/master-build/SUGGAPLAY-MASTER-BUILD-SPECIFICATION-v1.0.pdf`
2. `docs/master-build/README.md`
3. `docs/design-bible/00-design-tokens.md`
4. `docs/market-positioning/README.md`

## Build discipline

- Follow the **12-step build order** in the Master Build Spec exactly
- Stop after each step for review — do not skip ahead
- Explain implementation plan before coding
- Modify only files relevant to the current step

## Product rules

- Mobile app = the product. Website = marketing only
- Dark mode first, editorial luxury aesthetic
- No credits, tokens, or pay-per-message
- Never use "user" in copy — use Applicant / Member
- Brand line: "A private members' club for modern relationships."

## Stack (mobile)

Expo · React Native · TypeScript · Expo Router · NativeWind · React Query · Supabase · Stripe · RHF · Zod
